nsitive (BLAST-Pol). With its\nunprecedented mapping speed and resolution, BLAST-Pol will provide insights\ninto Galactic star-forming nurseries, and give the necessary link between the\nlarger, coarse resolution surveys and the narrow, resolved observations of\nstar-forming structures from space and ground based instruments being\ncommissioned in the next 5 years.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 May 2008 20:20:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Sep 2008 22:03:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
